		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.securityweek.com/?p=46789</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>A simple development setting bypassed protections designed to prevent unauthorized Android apps from accessing Microsoft account tokens, exposing billions of installations.</p>
